snippet.title: These Were The All-Time Surfing Moments Of The Year | Best Of 2020
snippet.description:
Well, that was a weird ride. Though it hasn't been easy, at least when we fixed our gaze on the ocean — or favorite place in the world – very little had changed. 

From Justine Dupont, Kai Lenny, Lucas Chumbo, and Conor Maguire's mind-blowing antics at Nazaré, Jaws and Mullaghmore to Carissa Moore, Caroline Marks, Jamie O'Brien, and Kanoa Igarashi's footwork on the world's most high-performance waves, we packed it all in here — and then some. 

For a full look at the edits we've sampled in the 2020 Best Of clip, check out the list below:

- Life of Kai: https://www.redbull.com/int-en/shows/life-of-kai

- Sessions: Nazaré: https://youtu.be/DRGdZJxZyJA

- Following: Julian Wilson: https://youtu.be/1EeLlx3jshM

- Chasing The Shot: Iceland: https://youtu.be/R2MXQFCLU1M

- The Other Side of Fear: https://www.redbull.com/int-en/films/the-other-side-of-fear

- Following: Kanoa Igarashi: https://youtu.be/xiaRs8LBfPM

- Sessions: Mundaka: https://youtu.be/YyQLN6WEBfI

- No Contest: https://youtu.be/w9zWqNu2vB8

- RAW: Mick Fanning: https://youtu.be/j30hptT5mm0

- No Contest: https://youtu.be/8sSbUg_qDQo

- Sessions: Bali: https://youtu.be/xvAsHHbrv1E

- The Rail Project: https://youtu.be/y2CTZ5GtMUA

- Sessions: Desert Point: https://youtu.be/e4MwBIOYypU

- Sessions: Jaws, Nov. 2020: https://youtu.be/agR1R0E72fo

- Sessions: Jaws, Jan. 2020: https://youtu.be/4Cgo5RZTcWk

- Taking Off: Broome: https://youtu.be/SYJgREKDYWk

- No Small Feat: https://youtu.be/i6kMDOEteqc

- RISS: https://youtu.be/plAtm41ewGk

- Following: Carissa Moore: https://youtu.be/d7kJlXJHZPY

- RAW: Eli Hanneman: https://youtu.be/_05vj_nUJv0

- Shaping Jordy: https://www.redbull.com/int-en/films/shaping-jordy

___
